{"word":"G2005 - ἐπιτελέω - epiteléō - ep-ee-tel-eh'-o - Accomplish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτελέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiteléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-tel-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accomplish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிறைவேற்று, பூரணப்படுத்து, முடிசெய், நடத்து, பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bring to an end, accomplish, perfect, execute, complete"},{"paragraph":"2. to appoint to, impose upon"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5055 - τελέω - teléō - tel-eh'-o/5055\">G5055</a>; to <i>fulfill further</i> (or <i>completely</i>), that is, <i>execute</i>; by implication to <i>terminate</i>, <i>undergo:</i> - accomplish, do, finish, (make) (perfect), perform (X -ance).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2005/2005\">G2005</a>, <a href=\"#/G3838/3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930/4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931/4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046/5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047/5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048/5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049/5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050/5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051/5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5052/5052\">G5052</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055/5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056/5056\">G5056</a>"}]}